com.ebay.lightning.core.store

Class ExecutionDataStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ebay.lightning.core.store.ExecutionDataStore

  • @Component
public class ExecutionDataStore
extends java.lang.Object
    The ExecutionDataStore holds the report for the requests executed. The report gets cleaned based on SystemConfig.getAuditCleanupFrequencyInSec() interval and SystemConfig.RetentionPolicy.
    Author:
    shashukla
